Z","msg":"竟然一查就查到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/044300_955622f4b8e13268488ce1f8f5152055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F044300_955622f4b8e13268488ce1f8f5152055.jpg&h=48a90945&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0aa8b3c50e30c273f8148e1aac9262f807023530","tid":315080,"uid":41325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:44:05.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - iagbnoks9s"},{"pid":"48b04f7b6279b61721b354c8b7dd78c85164ad65","tid":315080,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:46:17.000Z","msg":"我系你老母臭閪咩<br />\n上面咁多人系你老母都唔理<br />\n唔撚怪得要道符啦<br />\n用嚟保住你老母個閪唔好被我地屌爛呀"},{"pid":"f72c2396edbdddc8e2cdaf94f6a4ed559a9749b4","tid":315080,"uid":126103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲野如果你迷信既就唔好戴住<br />\n會好顯眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來真系戴得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3fa329b873a5bbe8f2236981466071a1faefba","tid":315080,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T20:54:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">系你老母個系<br />\n死返去5P啦仆街仔</span></span>"},{"pid":"f05c5833dcaea401614f79dc03dc711680c2bb8e","tid":315080,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:52:07.000Z","msg":"屌個系字好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你系夠未 專登咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df08ead4610ae7307aafdc3fdc20de6beaf462ff","tid":315080,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T23:09:18.000Z","msg":"[size=4]<span style=\"color: red;\">系你老母[</span>/size=4]<br />\n[size=5]<span s